title: Shark Tank Season 5
description:
Shark Tank is an American reality television series that premiered August 9, 2009 on ABC. Based on the worldwide television series format Dragons' Den that originally aired in Japan, Shark Tank has aspiring entrepreneurs make business presentations to a panel of potential investors, the so-called "sharks".

Episode 27 (Swimming with Sharks) was a special episode featuring behind the scenes activity in the production of Shark Tank as well as updates on the businesses of some entrepreneurs who appeared on prior shows.
